<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Verify your EcoLearn account</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9fafb; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 12px;">
          <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.12);">
            <tr>
              <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9488, #4ade80); padding: 36px; text-align: center; color: #ffffff;">
                <img src="https://img.icons8.com/external-flaticons-lineal-color-flat-icons/64/null/external-leaf-agriculture-flaticons-lineal-color-flat-icons.png" alt="EcoLearn" width="64" height="64" style="margin-bottom: 16px;" />
                <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 30px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Verify your EcoLearn account</h1>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 36px 40px 32px; color: #0f172a;">
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 16px;">
                  Hey <strong><%= name %></strong>, welcome to EcoLearn! We're thrilled to have you on board.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 24px;">
                  To keep your account secure and unlock access to quests, challenges, and badges, please confirm your email within the next 24 hours.
                </p>
                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin: 0 0 28px;">
                  <tr>
                    <td align="center">
                      <a href="<%= verificationLink %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 16px 38px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669, #22c55e); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 9999px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">
                        Verify email now
                      </a>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #475569; margin: 0 0 24px; text-align: center;">
                  This link will expire in <strong>24 hours</strong>. If it doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:<br />
                  <span style="word-break: break-all; color: #0f172a;"> <%= verificationLink %> </span>
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;">Letâ€™s do some good together ðŸŒ±<br /><strong>The EcoLearn Team</strong></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color: #f1f5f9; padding: 24px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b;">
                You're receiving this email because you signed up for EcoLearn. If you didn't create this account, you can safely ignore this email.
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
